Detailed Description

A Wordnik dictionary reference.

May be used to scope requests to a specific dictionary; not all data sources may support the full suite of pre-defined dictionaries.

Equality, Hashing, and Copying

WNDictionary instances implement NSObject's hash and isEqual methods, as well as the NSCopying protocol. Instances may be compared by value using NSObject::isEqual: and may be used as a key in NSDictionary.
